# ============================================================
# ACTA — Geospatial & Large Binary Assets
# ============================================================
# CRITICAL: Geographic raw data must NEVER enter Git history.
# Store locally in data/raw/ and reference via .env paths.
# ============================================================

# GeoJSON / Shapefiles / Raster
